lead_paragraph: DeAndre Jordan led six players in double figures with 22 points and 13 rebounds, and the Los Angeles Clippers defeated the Philadelphia 76ers 130-99 Saturday night for their season-high sixth straight victory.

headline.print_headline: Clippers Rout NBA-Worst 76ers 130-99 for 6th Straight Win
